  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK635">
<l>aṟaṉaṟin tāṉṟamainta collāṉeñ ñāṉṟun </l>
<l> tiṟaṉaṟintāṉ ṟērccit tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is the best helper (of the king) who understanding the duties, of the latter, is by his special learning, able to tender the fullest advice, and at all times conversant with the best method (of performing actions).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
